1
00:00:07,650 --> 00:00:08,750
Richard?
Richard?

2
00:00:08,750 --> 00:00:10,150
Over there is fine.
那儿挺好.

3
00:00:17,350 --> 00:00:18,350
Yvonne!
Yvonne!

4
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:20,600
I'm almost finished!
我快好了!

5
00:00:20,650 --> 00:00:25,350
Believe me, Douglas, Yvonne promised she would take the day off.
相信我, Douglas, Yvonne答应过今天要休息的.

6
00:00:25,450 --> 00:00:28,250
She said she had done enough work for one week.
她说她这一个星期做的事够多了.

7
00:00:29,750 --> 00:00:32,150
And now she is in there with a calculator.
但现在她却又在那里用计算器干活儿.

8
00:00:32,250 --> 00:00:33,772
I know. I know.
我知道. 我知道.

9
00:00:33,933 --> 00:00:35,874
Douglas, don't be shy.
Douglas, 别客气.

10
00:00:36,032 --> 00:00:38,473
This looks great.
看上去真不错.

11
00:00:39,154 --> 00:00:42,650
It smells fantastic.
闻起来好极了.

12
00:00:42,850 --> 00:00:45,350
Dig in. Yvonne!
吃吧. Yvonne!

13
00:00:45,450 --> 00:00:47,019
Two seconds!
两秒钟就好!

14
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:50,291
Douglas, Yvonne mentioned you were in Chicago.
Douglas, Yvonne说你去Chicago了. 

15
00:00:50,476 --> 00:00:54,671
Yeah. For a seminar on selling commercial property.
是的. 去参加一个关于出售商业资产的研讨会.

16
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:56,227
It was just a couple of days.
只待了几天.

17
00:00:56,372 --> 00:00:58,031
This is delicious.
味道好极.

18
00:00:58,231 --> 00:01:01,142
But the flight back was horrible.
但回程很糟糕.

19
00:01:01,305 --> 00:01:03,026
We flew through a huge storm.
我们飞行过程中经历了暴风雨.

20
00:01:03,210 --> 00:01:04,735
I hate airplanes.
我讨厌坐飞机.

21
00:01:04,925 --> 00:01:06,807
You told me you were over that.
你跟我说过你已经不怕了.

22
00:01:06,850 --> 00:01:08,492
Not when I hear these stories.
但我听不得这类事.

23
00:01:08,644 --> 00:01:10,100
This was pretty bad.
这次是很糟糕.

24
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:14,107
At one point, the flight attendants told us we had to take crash positions.
空中服务员一度曾告诉我们要做好应急准备.

25
00:01:14,230 --> 00:01:16,450
Oh, my god! You're kidding!
Oh, 天哪! 你是在开玩笑吧!

26
00:01:16,450 --> 00:01:19,602
No. And then the pilot came on and said we couldn't land.
不是. 然后驾驶员在广播中说我们无法降落.

27
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:21,150
It was absolutely terrifying.
那真是太可怕了.

28
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:23,800
Of course, statistically, it's very safe.
当然, 统计数字表明, 飞机是很安全的.

29
00:01:23,850 --> 00:01:26,587
Tell that to the people in the crash position.
去跟那些面临应急情况的人说吧.

30
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:31,920
Well, to be fair, I lived to tell the story. I am here.
Well, 说句公道话, 我还是活下来讲这番经历了. 我现在就安然无恙地在这里.

31
00:01:32,050 --> 00:01:35,650
But your wife isn't. Yvonne!
但你妻子不在. Yvonne!

32
00:01:35,750 --> 00:01:37,831
Yvonne, we ate all the food!
Yvonne, 我们可都吃光了!

33
00:01:37,950 --> 00:01:40,102
There's nothing left. You missed it.
一点都没有了. 你错过了这顿饭.

